Uses of Interface
io.github.hakkelt.ndarrays.NDArray

  • Packages that use NDArray 
    Package Description
    io.github.hakkelt.ndarrays
    General framework for N-dimensional arrays holding either complex or real values.
    io.github.hakkelt.ndarrays.basic
    Simple reference implementation for NDArrays backed by 1D array of primitive values.
